Dynamic Revenue Orchestrator (Generally Available)

Monitor Decomposition During Fulfillment

View and work within a graphical interface showing product decomposition. The Decomposition Viewer shows exactly how fulfillment order items were decomposed, helping to validate the correctness of order decomposition, as well as quickly troubleshoot any fallout.

Where: This feature is available in Lightning Experience in Developer, Enterprise, and Unlimited editions where Revenue Lifecycle Management is enabled.

How: From an order, click the Fulfillment Lines tab.
